data.description: Here's that new listing you've been waiting on! Come see this beautiful 3 sided brick home located in the Eagle's Bluff Subdivision. Convenient to everything you want: schools, tech college, shopping, grocery, gas stations and more. This home has a brand new HVAC unit, new paint throughout and brand new stainless steel kitchen appliances! As you enter you're greeted by a large living area with vaulted ceilings, a wood-burning fireplace and a formal dining room with plenty of natural light. The eat-in kitchen has plenty of cabinets for storage and a perfect spot for you breakfast table overlooking the backyard. The large master suite is very spacious and includes a very fancy Kohler walk-in tub and a walk-in closet. On the other side of this split bedroom floor plan you'll find 2 more bedrooms separated by a full bathroom. Step out back and you'll find a spacious wooden deck overlooking a large backyard with privacy fence  perfect for watching the kids and/or pets run and play. Like gardening? There's plenty of room for that too! The home and carpets have been professionally cleaned. Zoned for Perdue Elementary School, Mossy Creek Middle School and Houston County High school. This home is move-in ready and waiting for you and your family to make it your own! Call today to schedule a showing!!
